<header>
<%= render partial: "signup.header" %>
</header>
<main class= post-singnup1-main>
  <div class= post-singnup1-main__top>  
   会員情報入力
  </div>
  <div class= post-singnup1-main__bottom>
    <div class= post-singnup1-main__bottom__form>
      <%= form_with(model: @user, url: signup2_signup_index_path, method: :get,  local: true ) do |form| %>
      <div class= post-singnup1-nickname>
        <div class= post-singnup1-nickname__title>
          <div class= post-singnup1-nickname__title__text>ニックネーム</div>
          <div class= post-singnup1-nickname__title__must>必須</div>
        </div>
        <%= form.text_field :nickname, placeholder: "  例）メルカリ太郎", class: :"post-singnup1-nickname__form" %>
      </div>

      <div class= post-singnup1-email>
        <div class= post-singnup1-email__title>
          <div class= post-singnup1-email__title__text>メールアドレス</div>
          <div class= post-singnup1-email__title__must>必須</div>
        </div>
        <%= form.text_field :email, placeholder: "携帯どちらでも可", class: :"post-singnup1-email__form" %>
      </div>

      <div class= post-singnup1-password>
        <div class= post-singnup1-password__title>
          <div class= post-singnup1-password__title__text>パスワード</div>
          <div class= post-singnup1-password__title__must>必須</div>
        </div>
        <%= form.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", placeholder: "７文字以上の半角英数字", class: :"post-singnup1-password__form" %>
        <div class= post-singnup1-password__notice>
        ※英語と数字の両方を含めて設定してください
        </div>
        <%# <%= form.check_box :password,  class: :"post-singnup1-password__indication" %> %>
        <%= form.label :パスワードを表示する, class: :"post-singnup1-password__indication__label"%>

      <div class=post-singnup1-identification>
        <div class=post-singnup1-identification__h>本人確認</div>
        <div class=post-singnup1-identification__text>
        安心・安全にご利用いただくために、お客さまの本人<br>
        情報の登録にご協力ください。他のお客さまに公開さ<br>
        れることはありません。   
       </div>
      </div>

      <div class= post-singnup1-name-kanji>
        <div class= post-singnup1-name-kanji__title>
          <div class= post-singnup1-name-kanji__title__text>お名前（全角）</div>
          <div class= post-singnup1-name-kanji__title__must>必須</div>
        </div>
        <div class = post-singnup1-name-kanji__form>
          <%= form.text_field :family_name, placeholder: "例）山田", class: :"post-singnup1-name-kanji__form__family_name" %>
          <%= form.text_field :first_name, placeholder: "例）彩", class: :"post-singnup1-name-kanji__form__first_name" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      
      <div class= post-singnup1-name-kana>
        <div class= post-singnup1-name-kana__title>
          <div class= post-singnup1-name-kana__title__text>お名前カナ（全角）</div>
          <div class= post-singnup1-name-kana__title__must>必須</div>
        </div>
        <div class= post-singnup1-name-kanji__form>
          <%= form.text_field :family_name_kana, placeholder: "例）ヤマダ", class: :"post-singnup1-name-kanji__form__family_name" %>
          <%= form.text_field :first_name_kana, placeholder: "例）アヤ", class: :"post-singnup1-name-kanji__form__first_name" %>
        </div>
    </div>


      <div class= post-singnup1-birthday>
        <div class= post-singnup1-birthday__title>
          <div class= post-singnup1-birthday__title__text>生年月日</div>
          <div class= post-singnup1-birthday__title__must>必須</div>
        </div>
        <div class= post-singnup1-birthday__form>
          <label class= post-singnup1-birthday__form__select>
            <%= select_year(Date.today, start_year: Time.now.year, end_year: 1900, use_year_numbers: true) %>
          </label>
          <p class= post-singnup1-birthday__form__date>年</p>     
          <label class= post-singnup1-birthday__form__select>
            <%= select_month(Date.today, use_month_numbers: true) %>
          </label>
          <p class= post-singnup1-birthday__form__date>月</p>
          <label class= post-singnup1-birthday__form__select>
            <%= select_day(Date.today, use_day_numbers: true) %>
          </label>
          <p class= post-singnup1-birthday__form__date>日</p>
          </div>
        <div class= post-singnup1-birthday__notice>
        ※本人情報は正しく入力してください。会員登録後、<br>
        修正するにはお時間を頂く場合があります。
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class= post-singnup1-captcha>ロボットではありません</div>
      <div class= post-singnup1-agreement>
      「次へ進む」のボタンを押すことにより、<%= link_to "利用規約", "#", class: "post-singnup1-agreement__link"%>に<br>
      同意したものとみなします
      </div>
      <div class= post-singnup1-next>
      <%# <%= link_to "次に進む", "#", class: "post-singnup1-next__link" %>
        <label>
          <%= form.submit style: "display: none" %>
          <p class="post-singnup1-next__link">次へ進む</p>
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class= post-singnup1-about-registration>
      <%= link_to "本人情報の登録について>", "#", class: "post-singnup1-about-registration__link" %>  
      <% end %>
    </div>  
  </div>
</main>
<footer>
<%= render  partial: "signup.footer"%>
</footer>
